desc:
Elegant waterfront reserve living or an ideal investment.With superb harbour, Opera House and Harbour Bridge views, this whisper quiet, sundrenched apartment has grand proportions and is located on beautifual Cremorne  Point Reserve with the ferry almost at the door.Luxury living and still scope to improve. No stairs, lift to the door.NOTICE - COVID 19 GUIDELINES
DO NOT ATTEND THE INSPECTION IF YOU HAVE: FLU-LIKE SYMPTOMS, HAVE TESTED POSITIVE OR HAVE BEEN IN CONTACT WITH SOMEONE THAT HAS TESTED POSITIVE TO COVID-19PHYSICAL DISTANCING OF GREATER THAN 1.5 METRES MUST BE MAINTAINED AT ALL TIMES
